The '''SubLight Acceleration Motor''', also known as the '''SLAM''',<ref name="BMF 32">{{BuildFalconCite|32|Secrets of Spaceflight}}</ref> was an overdrive system that rerouted a [[sublight engine]]'s energy for acceleration bursts. The [[SRB42 sublight engine|SRB42]] engines of the ''[[Millennium Falcon]]'', a heavily customized [[YT-1300 light freighter|YT-1300f light freighter]], were equipped with one such device.<ref name="IncrediBuilds">''[[Star Wars: Millennium Falcon Deluxe Book and Model Set]]''</ref>

